HTML:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
     .led {
        position: relative;
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        border: 1px solid black;
      }
     .led::before,
     .led::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 50%;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        width: 50px;
        height: 50px;
        background-color: white;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      }
     .led::before {
        border-right: 3px solid black;
      }
     .led::after {
        border-left: 3px solid black;
      }
     .led:hover::before,
     .led:hover::after {
        background-color: black;
      }
     .led:hover {
        animation: blink 1s infinite;
      }
      @keyframes blink {
        50% {
          background-color: white;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="led"></div>
  </body>
</html>
```

